"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-01-matt-baker-commentating-olympic-gymnastics-21344997\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Matt Bakerisbest known for presenting Blue Peterfrom 1999 until 2006, BBC One'sCountryfilesince 2009 andThe One Showfrom 2011 to 2020 - but few people know he was also once a gymnast.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 70, \"end\": 77, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6528819347889186e-26, \"text\": \"BBC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheBBCpresenter commentating the gymnastics at the2024 Paris Olympicswas once a star of the sport himself.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 240, \"end\": 245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999713509, \"rank\": 2.878335362831466e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 46-year-old has also played a part inthe national broadcaster's coverage of gymnasticssince the 2008 Beijing Olympics, doing so again at Rio 2016, Tokyo 2020 and this year's event too.\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 444, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.997353324856252, \"rank\": 0.0026536390632660133, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, for those unsure why Matt was part of the commentating team,he once explainedhis connection to the sport.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  'For all those asking\\u2026 here's some clippings from my old scrap book!'\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"he posted on Instagram in 2021 along with a photo of newspaper clippings showing his past achievements.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5383154421138186e-29, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the headlines read 'Gymnast reaches perfection', with the article explaining how he'd been awarded a 10 for one of his routines as a 12-year-old and was believed to be the only competitor from the region to gain that mark.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: 'As a lad gymnastics was my life\\u2026it taught me the simple recipe if you work hard, you get a result.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Without my sport I would never be where I am today \\u2026 #gymnastics #workhard.'\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Born and raised in Easington in County Durham where his father ran a newsagent's shop, Matt began competing as a gymnast whilst at school.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Easington_District\", \"score\": 0.9999777715585336, \"rank\": 2.2228931411988658e-05, \"text\": \"Easington\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Easington_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Easington_District\"}, {\"begin\": 1298, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Durham\", \"score\": 0.9999999978126652, \"rank\": 2.090269293875323e-09, \"text\": \"County Durham\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Durham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Durham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, aged 14, he was forced to give it up after being diagnosed with anaemia.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He later studied drama and was then cast in Blue Peter, a role that saw him win two Baftas for Best Children's Presenter two years in a row and a Royal Television Society award.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blue_Peter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.422095112444741e-25, \"text\": \"Blue Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blue_Peter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blue_Peter\"}, {\"begin\": 1635, \"end\": 1659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Television_Society\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Television Society\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Television_Society\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Television_Society\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He later competed on Strictly Come Dancing in 2010.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the Olympics Matt spoke about his past experience after some questioned his expertise.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It makes me laugh when people ask, \\\"Why is the guy from Countryfile commentating on gymnastics?\\\"\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1875, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Countryfile\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Countryfile\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Countryfile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Countryfile\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But yes, I love the eclectic mix of things that I do and have done,' he told TV Times.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2002, 